      • callBackOnModuleReset

        public final void callBackOnModuleReset​(@NotNull
                                        Consumer<SModule> callback)
        #attach and #detach are designed final, doing the simplest thing (resetting the field #myModule) It appears that sometimes a client of this class needs to perform a custom initialization when the owning module is being changed. We do not want to go back to overridable #attach, instead offering to provide a single callback in a separate method below.
        Parameters:
        callback - -- will be called in this method and on each module re-set.
